    "Title": "Cargo Transfer from Shuttered Facility",
    "Description": "RED WIND LINEHAUL \n'YOUR GOODS IN GOOD HANDS' \n----------------------------    \n\nASD reached out to us as it seems one of their old labs, <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>, still has some cargo being stored there they want to get their hands on.\n\nYou would fly there in a ship that can handle containers up to <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize)</EM4> in size, land in the hangar, load up from the freight elevator, and then transport it all back to <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>. \n\nJust be sure to keep your head on swivel while you\u2019re at the facility and try not to let your curiosity get the better of you Abandoned sites like this can be home to all sort of nastiness.  And don't forget to pack a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> to bring along. \n\nBE YOUR BEST \u2013 Take pride in the work you do and you\u2019ll do work to be proud of.",
